headline: Healthcare’s Momentum Gathers Steam. 3 Stocks With Bullish Charts.
summary: FEATURE  Healthcare stocks are recovering strongly as the year winds down. The is the best-performing of 11 major S&P sector funds over the past week, month, and three-month periods.  The appeal of this group is its variety.
